AttributeList.Text: ============================================================================= The TrfIn function is a standard FB to be used in all transport functions (as roller, cross-section, …) to execute an IN transfer in automatic Mode or in manual Mode. The module will generate the signal O_TrfInCmd to be used by the Motor loop block to steer the Motor. It will also generate handshake signals : "O_Ready To Receive (Ready to Receive) to inform previous equipement that this equipement is ready to receive a new body, "O_Arrived to inform the previous equipment that transfer is done, "O_Finish to inform the master sequence that the transport function has finished. =============================================================================
